<plot>Documentary about the last years of the life of singer 'Jacques Brel' (qv) on the Marquesas Islands. 'Maddly Bamy' (qv), his last love, and a number of locals talk about the years Brel spend on the island while the camera shows us the beauty of the island. Of course, several songs of Brel can be heard throughout the documentary.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?272448</url></doc>
